---
import SearchBar from "../ui/SearchBar.astro";
import Light3DScene from "../ui/Light3DScene.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<section class="rw-hero-premium relative isolate overflow-hidden border-b border-rw-ink/10 bg-rw-ink text-rw-white dark:border-rw-white/10 dark:bg-rw-ink dark:text-rw-white">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-80">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-rw-ink/15"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-24 h-px w-full rotate-[-3deg] bg-rw-ink/8"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-24 right-0 h-px w-full rotate-[2deg] bg-rw-horizon/12"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto grid min-h-[88dvh] max-w-[1500px] grid-cols-1 gap-8 px-4 pb-16 pt-10 sm:px-6 sm:pb-24 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:px-10 lg:pt-16">
    <div class="order-1 flex flex-col justify-end lg:col-span-5 lg:pb-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <div class="mb-7 flex items-center gap-4 font-ui text-[12px] font-black tracking-[0.02em] text-rw-gold">
          <span class="h-px w-16 bg-rw-gold/55"></span>
          <span data-i18n="hero.kicker">Revista de rutas raras</span>
        </div>

        <h1 data-i18n="hero.title" class="text-balance font-display text-[clamp(2.85rem,12vw,7.1rem)] font-black leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.035em] text-rw-white dark:text-rw-white">
          El mundo es más raro de lo que imaginas
        </h1>

        <p data-i18n="hero.copy" class="text-pretty mt-7 max-w-[35rem] font-body text-xl leading-[1.65] text-rw-sand/82 sm:text-2xl">
          Crónicas de fronteras absurdas, carreteras secundarias, islas sin coches y ciudades que parecen inventadas, explicadas para viajar sin perder el criterio.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 max-w-xl rounded-[.9rem] border border-rw-gold/18 bg-rw-sand/10 p-2 shadow-[0_24px_70px_-48px_rgba(0,0,0,.85)] backdrop-blur">
          <SearchBar />
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-7 gap-y-4">
          <a href={`${base}blog/`} class="rw-luxury-link text-rw-white"><span data-i18n="hero.cta.primary">Leer la revista</span></a>
          <a href={`${base}#planificador-rutas`} class="rw-luxury-link text-rw-horizon"><span data-i18n="hero.cta.secondary">Diseñar una ruta</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="order-2 lg:col-span-7">
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[760px] lg:mr-0">
        <div class="absolute -left-4 top-10 z-20 hidden w-48 border border-rw-gold/24 bg-rw-ink/88 p-4 font-ui text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.04em] text-rw-gold shadow-[0_24px_70px_-48px_rgba(0,0,0,.9)] backdrop-blur md:block">
          <span data-i18n="hero.badge.title">Archivo vivo</span>
          <span data-i18n="hero.badge.copy" class="mt-2 block font-body text-base normal-case leading-snug tracking-normal text-rw-sand">Rutas que se leen como una historia y se usan como una guía.</span>
        </div>

        <figure class="rw-depth-frame relative overflow-hidden rounded-[.95rem] border border-rw-gold/18 bg-rw-sand/10 p-3 shadow-[0_40px_110px_-70px_rgba(0,0,0,.98)]" data-rw-tilt-lite>
          <Light3DScene />
          <img
            src="/images/route-mountain.svg"
            alt="Visual editorial de una ruta de montaña"
            class="h-[45vh] min-h-[320px] w-full rounded-[.6rem] object-cover object-center saturate-[0.82] contrast-[1.04] transition duration-[900ms] hover:scale-[1.025] sm:h-[52vh] sm:min-h-[390px]"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <figcaption class="mt-3 flex flex-col gap-2 px-1 pb-1 font-ui text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.03em] text-rw-sand/62 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <span data-i18n="hero.caption.left">Atlas visual, edición semanal</span>
            <span data-i18n="hero.caption.right" class="text-rw-horizon">Rutas que no salen primeras en Google</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>

        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 right-4 z-20 w-[min(86%,360px)] rounded-[.9rem] border border-rw-gold/20 bg-rw-white px-5 py-4 text-rw-ink shadow-[0_28px_80px_-45px_rgba(0,0,0,.95)] sm:right-10">
          <p data-i18n="hero.note.title" class="font-display text-2xl font-bold leading-tight">Primera regla editorial</p>
          <p data-i18n="hero.note.copy" class="mt-2 font-ui text-sm leading-relaxed text-rw-ocean/78">Si una ruta no cambia cómo miras el mapa, no merece portada.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
